text: Helen Ruth Elam (born July 18, 1928), better known as Baddiewinkle or Baddie Winkle, is an American internet personality. She became a popular internet celebrity in her 80s. She is known for her social media tagline "Stealing Your Man Since 1928". She is also known for being an activist for legalizing medical marijuana. ==References== Category:1928 births Category:Living people Category:American Internet celebrities Category:Models from Kentucky
